race.comment: SILK SONIC (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (30.00) at this track in a Other. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Top prospect. TIME AFTER TIME (5) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (30.04) at this track in a Other over 512m. Can measure up. JUST JOHNNIE (4) missed the frame latest when fifth at this track (23.63) but scored three back at this track (23.21). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. A big run wouldn't surprise. OREGON CALDWELL (7) must be respected at his pet track and distance.
